### 6. CREATE TABLE - Duplicate Table Number (Error)
### ============================================
POST {{baseUrl}}/tables
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

{
  "tableNumber": 1,
  "capacity": 4,
